name: Uint8ClampedArray.BYTES_PER_ELEMENT
description: Returns a number value of the element size. 1 in the case of Uint8ClampedArray.

name: Uint8ClampedArray.prototype.BYTES_PER_ELEMENT
description: Returns a number value of the element size. 1 in the case of a Uint8ClampedArray.

name: Uint8ClampedArray.prototype.constructor
description: The constructor function that created the instance object. For Uint8ClampedArray instances, the initial value is the Uint8ClampedArray constructor.
